				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Nerfing and AEing<a name="53046"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 21 04 1:41 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>The &quot;nerf&quot; they speak of was some time back when SoE corrected an error in programming that caused our AA Extended Notes to affect any and all AE type songs.  The AA was never meant to work on any but beneficial songs, therefore it was not a nerf.
<br />

<br />
There was a change some months back where mobs started to go off in strange directions at 70% health in large kites.  Some consider this a nerf, and it well may be.  Best thing to do is just be careful and ready to hightail it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
